	<h2>Use cases</h2>
	<ul class="features-grid">
		<li class="feature">
			<h3>Agent screen pop</h3>
			<p>Display a caller name in CRM or helpdesk workflows before the conversation starts.</p>
		</li>
		<li class="feature">
			<h3>Inbound screening</h3>
			<p>Use caller identity as one signal in spam, fraud, and escalation decisions.</p>
		</li>
		<li class="feature">
			<h3>Routing context</h3>
			<p>Route known business callers, customers, or anonymous callers into different queues or workflows.</p>
		</li>
		<li class="feature">
			<h3>Batch hygiene</h3>
			<p>Run lists through batch lookup before a campaign, migration, or data-cleanup project.</p>
		</li>
	</ul>
</section>

